Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,見つけたいでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,儚い story 繋ぐ　明日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on now, come on, on a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,探してる鍵を (Where's the key?)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Just move, and go find out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Let's go, come on, come on, on a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ 知りたいでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,描く場所に辿り着くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on, now, come on, on a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:38.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,運命が呼び寄せた導きの証
